snippet.title: Launch Trailer - Official Call of Duty: Black Ops 2 Video
snippet.description: Dive into the near-future world of 2025, unraveling a generation-spanning story that has led to a global conflict unlike ever before. Call of Duty: Black Ops 2 arrives 11.13.12. Stay updated on all of the latest Black Ops 2 news by following us on Facebook (http://www.facebook.com/codblackops) and Twitter (@CallofDuty and @Treyarch).
